<plot>This short concert special covers the Copenhagen leg of Bruce Springsteen's Tunnel of Love tour on 25 July 1988. It features a small number of performances from the concert, brief interviews with some of the audience and, remarkably, amateur footage of a casual street performance Springsteen gave (alledgedly recorded on 23 July accompanied by street guitarist John Magnusson).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?080244</url></doc>
